title: Former 'Game Of Thrones' Star Rose Leslie Thinks Jon Snow Is 'Deader Than Dead'
text:
Former 'Game Of Thrones' Star Rose Leslie Thinks Jon Snow Is 'Deader Than Dead' The actress, who played Ygritte, says Snow's fate is sealed. Ryan Buxton Senior Editor, HuffPost Live Posted: 10/12/2015 04:44 PM EDT | Edited: 14 minutes ago 
Spoilers ahead if you have yet to watch "Game of Thrones." 
Rose Leslie hasn't been on the "Game of Thrones" set since her character, Ygritte, met her demise in Season 4, but she's still totally immersed in the "GoT' world. Despite keeping busy with other projects, like her new film " The Last Witch Hunter ," Leslie told HuffPost Live that she stays up-to-date will all things Westeros, including last season's shocking conclusion . With rumors swirling that we haven't seen the last of Jon Snow, host Alyona Minkovski asked Leslie on Monday for her take on Jon's fate -- and it's bleak. 
Watch Leslie weigh in on Jon Snow's future above, and click here for her full HuffPost Live conversation.
